'''念珠菌症'''（{{lang|en|Candidiasis}}）是[[假丝酵母属|假丝酵母属]]（[[酵母菌|酵母菌]]的一種）所造成的[[真菌病|黴菌感染]]<ref name=CDC2014Can>{{cite web|title=Candidiasis|url=http://www.cdc.gov/fungal/diseases/candidiasis/|website=cdc.gov|accessdate=28 December 2014|date=February 13, 2014|archive-date=2014-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141229221331/http://www.cdc.gov/fungal/diseases/candidiasis/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在感染[[口腔|口腔]]時，就會引發鵝口瘡（Thrush）<ref name=CDC2014Can/>。症狀和病徵包括在舌頭、口腔以及咽喉的部位出現小白點<ref name=CDC2014OralS>{{cite web|title=Symptoms of Oral Candidiasis|url=http://www.cdc.gov/fungal/diseases/candidiasis/thrush/symptoms.html|website=cdc.gov|accessdate=28 December 2014|date=February 13, 2014|archive-date=2014-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141229221255/http://www.cdc.gov/fungal/diseases/candidiasis/thrush/symptoms.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也可能產生例如酸痛或吞嚥困難等的其他徵候<ref name=CDC2014OralS/>。當它感染陰道，就會引起一般稱作酵母菌感染（Yeast infection）的疾病<ref name=CDC2014Can/>，會有包括外陰部搔癢、灼熱感有時甚至會有類似起司塊狀的分泌物從陰道流出的情形<ref>{{cite web|title=Symptoms of Genital / Vulvovaginal Candidiasis|url=http://www.cdc.gov/fungal/diseases/candidiasis/genital/symptoms.html|website=cdc.gov|accessdate=28 December 2014|date=February 13, 2014|archive-date=2014-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141229221253/http://www.cdc.gov/fungal/diseases/candidiasis/genital/symptoms.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，陰莖的感染較不常見，但若發生感染，則也會有搔癢感<ref name=CDC2014OralS/>。有極少數的病例，可能會引發全身性的感染，且會因不同感染部位而產生不同病徵與[[發燒|發燒]]症狀<ref>{{cite web|title=Symptoms of Invasive Candidiasis|url=http://www.cdc.gov/fungal/diseases/candidiasis/invasive/symptoms.html|website=cdc.gov|accessdate=28 December 2014|date=February 13, 2014|archive-date=2014-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141229230002/http://www.cdc.gov/fungal/diseases/candidiasis/invasive/symptoms.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
<!-- 成因 -->
念珠菌屬的真菌中約有二十種會造成感染，其中最常見的是[[白色念珠菌|白色念珠菌]]<ref name=CDC2014Can/>。常見的感染部位是口部，常出現在一個月內的新生兒、老人，以及[[免疫缺陷|免疫系統較弱]]的病患<!-- <ref name=CDC2014RiskO/> -->。免疫系統較弱的病患包括[[愛滋病|愛滋病]]患、接受[[器官移植|器官移植]]者、[[糖尿病|糖尿病]]患者，以及[[口服|口服]][[皮質類固醇|皮質類固醇]]者<!-- <ref name=CDC2014RiskO> -->。其他風險因子包含使用[[假牙|假牙]]，以及接受[[抗生素|抗生素]]治療者<ref name=CDC2014RiskO>{{cite web|title=Risk & Prevention|url=http://www.cdc.gov/fungal/diseases/candidiasis/thrush/risk-prevention.html|website=cdc.gov|accessdate=28 December 2014|date=February 13, 2014|archive-date=2021-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210315151036/https://www.cdc.gov/fungal/diseases/candidiasis/thrush/risk-prevention.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。陰道感染通常發生於[[懷孕|妊娠期]]，特別是在免疫功能低下並使用抗生素者<ref name=CDC2014VP>{{cite web|title=People at Risk for Genital / Vulvovaginal Candidiasis|url=http://www.cdc.gov/fungal/diseases/candidiasis/genital/risk-prevention.html|website=cdc.gov|accessdate=28 December 2014|date=February 13, 2014|archive-date=2014-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141229230132/http://www.cdc.gov/fungal/diseases/candidiasis/genital/risk-prevention.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。全身性感染的風險因子包含進過[[加護病房|加護病房]]、手術後的那段恢復期、{{le|出生時體重不到標準的嬰兒| low birth weight infant}}，以及免疫系統低下者<ref name=CDC2014IP>{{cite web|title=People at Risk for Invasive Candidiasis|url=http://www.cdc.gov/fungal/diseases/candidiasis/invasive/risk-prevention.html|website=cdc.gov|accessdate=28 December 2014|date=February 13, 2014|archive-date=2014-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141229230136/http://www.cdc.gov/fungal/diseases/candidiasis/invasive/risk-prevention.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

<!-- 預防及治療 -->
避免口腔感染的方法包含：讓免疫能力較差的人使用含[[洗必泰|洗必泰]]（防腐消毒藥）的漱口水漱口、[[氣喘|氣喘患者]]於使用吸入性[[類固醇|類固醇]]後漱口<!--Efforts to prevent infections of the mouth include the use of [[chlorhexidine|chlorhexidine]] mouth wash in those with poor immune function and washing out the mouth following the use of inhaled steroids.--><ref name=CDC2014Otx/>；陰道經常感染的患者則可使用[[益生菌|益生菌]]來治療<ref name=CDC2014VP/>。口腔感染的患者塗抹[[克黴樂|克黴樂]]或[[耐絲菌素|耐絲菌素]]通常有效，但若上述治療無效則可以口服或注射[[氟可那挫|氟可那挫]]、[[伊曲康唑|伊曲康唑]]，或[[两性霉素B|两性霉素B]]等藥物<ref name=CDC2014Otx>{{cite web|title=Treatment & Outcomes of Oral Candidiasis|url=http://www.cdc.gov/fungal/diseases/candidiasis/thrush/treatment.html|website=cdc.gov|accessdate=28 December 2014|date=February 13, 2014|archive-date=2021-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210315155323/https://www.cdc.gov/fungal/diseases/candidiasis/thrush/treatment.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。陰道感染目前已知有許多抗真菌藥物可以治療，包含[[克黴樂|克黴樂]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Treatment & Outcomes of Genital / Vulvovaginal Candidiasis|url=http://www.cdc.gov/fungal/diseases/candidiasis/genital/treatment.html|website=cdc.gov|accessdate=28 December 2014|date=February 13, 2014|archive-date=2014-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141229230134/http://www.cdc.gov/fungal/diseases/candidiasis/genital/treatment.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。全身性的感染則通常以靜脈注射給予[[兩性黴素B|兩性黴素B]]治療<ref>{{cite web|title=Treatment & Outcomes of Invasive Candidiasis|url=http://www.cdc.gov/fungal/diseases/candidiasis/invasive/treatment.html|website=cdc.gov|accessdate=28 December 2014|date=February 13, 2014|archive-date=2021-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210318081821/https://www.cdc.gov/fungal/diseases/candidiasis/invasive/treatment.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，對於易受感染的特定族群則可能會預防性地給予抗真菌藥物<ref name=CDC2014IP/>。

<!-- 流行病學 -->
出生不到一個月的嬰兒中，6%會有口腔型的念珠菌感染<!-- <ref name=Oral2014Stat/> -->。正接受[[化療|化療]]的癌症病患其感染機率會有20%，[[愛滋病|愛滋病]]患也有20％的感染風險<ref name=Oral2014Stat>{{cite web|title=Oral Candidiasis Statistics|url=http://www.cdc.gov/fungal/diseases/candidiasis/thrush/statistics.html|website=cdc.gov|accessdate=28 December 2014|date=February 13, 2014|archive-date=2014-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141229221333/http://www.cdc.gov/fungal/diseases/candidiasis/thrush/statistics.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。差不多有四分之三的女性曾在一生中感染過念珠菌症<ref>{{cite web|title=Genital / vulvovaginal candidiasis (VVC)|url=http://www.cdc.gov/fungal/diseases/candidiasis/genital/index.html|website=cdc.gov|accessdate=28 December 2014|date=February 13, 2014|archive-date=2014-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141229221412/http://www.cdc.gov/fungal/diseases/candidiasis/genital/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。全身性的感染並不常見，通常只見於暴露在危險因子中的患者<ref>{{cite web|title=Invasive Candidiasis Statistics|url=http://www.cdc.gov/fungal/diseases/candidiasis/invasive/statistics.html|website=cdc.gov|accessdate=28 December 2014|date=February 13, 2014|archive-date=2014-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141229221416/http://www.cdc.gov/fungal/diseases/candidiasis/invasive/statistics.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。這些疾病在學術的名稱分別為'''念珠菌症'''、'''念珠菌性陰道炎'''（moniliasis）還有'''卵霉菌病'''（oidiomycosis）<ref name="Andrews">{{cite book |author=James, William D.; Berger, Timothy G. |title=Andrews' Diseases of the Skin: clinical Dermatology |url=https://archive.org/details/andrewsdiseasess00mdwi_659 |publisher=Saunders Elsevier|pages=[https://archive.org/details/andrewsdiseasess00mdwi_659/page/308 308]–311|year=2006 |isbn=0-7216-2921-0|display-authors=etal}}</ref>。

==病原特性==
念珠菌是一種[[真菌|真菌]]，屬[[酵母菌目|酵母菌目]](Saccharomycetales)，具酵母型或假菌絲型雙相，酵母型為圓形或橢圓形，可產生芽生分生孢子。研究已發現超過150種念珠菌，有9種可感染人類。念珠菌對人類是一種伺機性病原，喜愛酸性環境常存於人體的口腔、皮膚、消化道、陰道等黏膜組織和臟器中，人體中最常見的為[[白色念珠菌|白色念珠菌]]（''Candida albicans''）。<ref name="cdc">[http://web.cdc.gov.tw/public/Attachment/8123017471199.pdf 第四十六章念珠菌症] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090507002842/http://web.cdc.gov.tw/public/Attachment/8123017471199.pdf |date=2009-05-07 }}</ref>

==種類==
人類可能因為住院期間接觸到受汙染的醫療器材、藥品而發生[[血液|血液]]感染，亦可能因為[[母乳餵養|哺乳]]時與嬰兒口腔接觸而發生皮膚感染，或[[性交|性交]]時男方的[[精液|精液]]糖分太高，念珠菌陰道炎容易發生在成年女性身上。

除此之外[[懷孕|懷孕]]、[[糖尿病|糖尿病]]、服用[[抗生素|抗生素]]和服用使身體免疫力下降的藥品，亦有可能增加念珠菌症的感染風險。<ref name="cdc"/><ref name="ntu">[http://ntuh.mc.ntu.edu.tw/bh/EDU/%E5%BF%B5%E7%8F%A0%E8%8F%8C%E9%99%B0%E9%81%93%E7%82%8E_%E7%8E%8B%E6%B3%89%E5%8B%B3%E9%86%AB%E5%B8%AB.doc 念珠菌陰道炎]{{dead link|date=2018年2月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }} - 台大醫院王泉勳醫師</ref>

==症狀==
念珠菌菌血症，感染時會發生發燒、心跳過快、呼吸急促、低血壓等類似細菌性敗血症症狀，死亡率達40-60%。<ref name="cdc"/>

罹患念珠菌陰道炎的患者陰道分泌物會增加，伴隨[[女陰|外陰]]搔癢症狀，由於[[月經|月經]]來潮時陰道環境偏鹼，症狀會稍微減輕。[[女陰|外陰部]]的念珠菌感染，若在性交時直接接觸而傳染。
==治療==
不同的症狀和不同感染菌種的念珠菌症，常選擇的藥物包括Amphotericin B，Fluconazole(有抑菌功能)，Liposomal amphotericin B，Voriconazole，Caspofungin等。<ref name="cdc"/>

外陰部感染可利用止癢藥物減輕症狀，並依醫師指示的濃度和方法，使用[[碳酸氫鈉|碳酸氫鈉]](小蘇打)溶液清洗外陰部。因其他疾病引起的念珠菌症，應同時改善該疾病。<ref name="ntu"/>

==預防==
為了預防侵入性念珠菌症，應加強自身的免疫力。

念珠菌喜愛悶熱潮溼的環境，預防皮膚感染型的念珠菌症，可穿清爽透氣吸汗材質等純棉或蠶絲製<ref name="ntu"/><ref>[http://www.silk.com.tw/tw/site/silk.php 蠶絲特性] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090630034344/http://www.silk.com.tw/tw/site/silk.php |date=2009-06-30 }}</ref>的貼身內衣褲，注意經常更換清洗，避免[[人造纖維|人造纖維]]材質的貼身衣物或緊身的[[牛仔褲|牛仔褲]]。

